### Walkabout

Participants walked a route through Anaheim Convention Center using **AVIV ScoutRoute** to collect on-the-ground pedestrian infrastructure observations, submitted to the **CSUN 2026** workspace.

#### Route

Anaheim Marriott to Anaheim GardenWalk

- **Distance**: 0.75 miles

[AccessMap](https://www.accessmap.app/dir?wp=-117.918313_33.799592%27-117.911555_33.8051782&region=ca.anaheim&lon=-117.9160288&lat=33.8023852&z=16.85&sa=1&mu=0.14&md=0.14&ab=0&aps=0)

